510
00:30:04,092 --> 00:30:05,816
<i>Vou apenas relaxar.</i>

511
00:30:07,091 --> 00:30:09,849
<i>Vamos lá, acalme-se.</i>

512
00:30:10,605 --> 00:30:13,086
Conte de dez a zero.

513
00:30:13,111 --> 00:30:16,750
<i>Dez, nove, oito,</i>

514
00:30:16,775 --> 00:30:19,963
<i>sete, seis, cinco,</i>

515
00:30:19,988 --> 00:30:23,982
<i>quatro, três, dois, um...</i>

516
00:30:24,007 --> 00:30:27,120
<i>Não consigo ver.</i>

517
00:30:28,485 --> 00:30:29,809
<i>Onde estou?</i>

518
00:30:31,985 --> 00:30:33,446
