525
00:30:54,851 --> 00:30:56,862
<i>Não sei
o que acontece comigo!</i>

526
00:30:58,409 --> 00:31:00,658
<i>Olá?</i>

527
00:31:01,226 --> 00:31:03,212
<i>Tem alguém aí?</i>

528
00:31:03,237 --> 00:31:05,031
<i>Olá?</i>

529
00:31:08,797 --> 00:31:11,002
Desculpe.

530
00:31:14,542 --> 00:31:18,463
